"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641278428,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"82ZA-rhY87KPUvkxKQ3qtJna4vJIrePKgCWhZBBPEBY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf5478Ed288cFb3bBEE08EBabE1F1C6757600746e\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"GVf7k11pCPS-MzD0tCqf7K0jV2liUeF1jmLuXR44ZBU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"N0dYf-Nquiyv-3JFDw28z2vpJ5bKQT6CpzeTGTGPTJY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"VrVDEi0kAZmw6cY5BYrg6d7KtX3jY3AZgx_BLE5QqocFZQh4CXOGCMqZphfRAaZT9hzEnyBCE98wILnpSte1MQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x80c992d3522887d4ad741ce2a7898f761154d008ff235a8dff89fe11567de249543ff9d305858256595452ba0efbcf04d0422f2af5fe0a459781440a37b3d6f31b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"GVf7k11pCPS-MzD0tCqf7K0jV2liUeF1jmLuXR44ZBU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"N0dYf-Nquiyv-3JFDw28z2vpJ5bKQT6CpzeTGTGPTJY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi